{"id":"api/platform-browser/REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY","title":"REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser/REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY\", \"name\": \"REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser\">@angular/platform-browser</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/platform-browser/src/dom/dom_renderer.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L53-L56\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/platform-browser/src/dom/dom_renderer.ts#L53-L56\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"remove_styles_on_component_destroy\">REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY#remove_styles_on_component_destroy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">一個<a href=\"guide/glossary#di-token\" title=\"DI 代幣定義\">DI 令牌</a>，指示是否應從 DOM 中刪除已銷燬元件的樣式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A <a href=\"guide/glossary#di-token\" title=\"DI token definition\">DI token</a> that indicates whether styles\nof destroyed components should be removed from DOM.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/platform-browser/REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY\" class=\"code-anchor\">REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY</a>: <a href=\"api/core/InjectionToken\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectionToken</a>&lt;boolean&gt;;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">預設情況下，該值設定為 <code>false</code>。這將在下一個主要版本中更改。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">By default, the value is set to <code>false</code>. This will be changed in the next major version.</p>\n\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-browser\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/InjectionToken\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY#description\n - api/platform-browser/REMOVE_STYLES_ON_COMPONENT_DESTROY#remove_styles_on_component_destroy\n - guide/glossary#di-token\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/platform-browser/src/dom/dom_renderer.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L53-L56\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/platform-browser/src/dom/dom_renderer.ts#L53-L56\n-->"}